title: Bring that Same Fake Energy
itunes:title: Bring that Same Fake Energy
description:
1/22/19 - Today on the show we opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners would want their spouse to give them fake good energy when they come home after work ,after a video of writer Nikki Giovanni telling James Baldwin that she would rather have her spouse fake being happy with her like he does at work. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Mike Pence for using MLK speech building on building a wall. Moreover, we opened up the phone lines to see what is the craziest thing they ever did for their job.
